{"tid":2094524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雷鼎鳴：多人移民是好事  令樓價下跌","createTime":"2020-07-04T16:53:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T17:27:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ba87d1e5e6c555f2e9a2117b7e3109d8486182dc","tid":2094524,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T16:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org/i/s/static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200704/_2020070418420575099.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic-stheadline-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fi%2Fs%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200704%2F_2020070418420575099.jpg&h=a6544550&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國參眾兩院通過《香港自治法案》，或會對香港實施制裁，科技大學經濟學系前系主任雷鼎鳴出席一個活動時表示，本港出口到美國的產品比例少，相信影響不大。<br />\n<br />\n他又指港區國安法實施後，部份人選擇移民外國，若有逾30萬人，或會令本港樓價下跌。「要足夠多人離開才可以，兩、三萬人離開都不夠，最好二、三十萬以上的人離開。弄走一些沒用的人」<br />\n<br />\n他又相信，使不少職位出現真空，部份人往上流機會增加，「願意留在香港的、又有正確思想的香港年輕人，他們有空間升級。」甚至吸納內地人才及國際科技專才，是一件好事。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://hd.stheadline .com/news/realtime/hk/1811644/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E9%9B%B7%E9%BC%8E%E9%B3%B4-%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E6%98%AF%E5%A5%BD%E4%BA%8B-%E6%88%96%E6%9C%83%E4%BB%A4%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8B%E8%B7%8C</code></pre>"},{"pid":"3af79a6033642305b0ab4e45f4becb1e575f45ec","tid":2094524,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T16:54:34.000Z","msg":"Agger<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ca7f486056e632a59f6d677834bc6c8e0b7751c","tid":2094524,"uid":2054,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsdb.memehk.com/img/post/18861_dsjbnfgjk234tr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsdb.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F18861_dsjbnfgjk234tr.png&h=cc8f0caa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40ad8f12155e6831c